{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773351814866,"sessionID":"ses_31c0172a9ffeekk99N9QZhhvnC","part":{"id":"prt_ce401303a001wqlCfJtR1jw1K9","sessionID":"ses_31c0172a9ffeekk99N9QZhhvnC","messageID":"msg_ce4012413001We6QBCpbhOli1o","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01JhT88g5gjN9McwS6KpuUTU","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git commit -m \"feat(toon-output): add TOON format spec and formatter module\n\nDesign the Token-Optimized Output Notation (TOON) format:\n- Pipe-delimited fields, no quotes/braces/whitespace padding\n- 2-char status codes (BL, IP, DN, etc.)\n- 1-char priority codes (C, H, M, L, W)\n- 1-char difficulty codes (T, E, M, H, V)\n- Self-describing legend via toonLegend()\n- Encoding functions for all data types: features, subtasks, wave status,\n  verification results, check results, archive results, command schemas\n\nUpdate OutputFormat type to include 'toon' as third option.\nAdd auto-detect heuristic via WOMBO_AGENT=1 env var.\nUpdate output/outputError/outputMessage helpers for toon format.\"","description":"Commit subtask 1: TOON format spec and formatter"},"output":"[feature/toon-output 3442b3b] feat(toon-output): add TOON format spec and formatter module\n 2 files changed, 669 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 src/lib/toon.ts\n","title":"Commit subtask 1: TOON format spec and formatter","metadata":{"output":"[feature/toon-output 3442b3b] feat(toon-output): add TOON format spec and formatter module\n 2 files changed, 669 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 src/lib/toon.ts\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit subtask 1: TOON format spec and formatter","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773351814858,"end":1773351814866}}}}
